	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />There shouldn't be problems with ROM based (hardware) codes (including for games with SA-1 since regardless of the physical ROM, it's accessed by the CPU the same way) but RAM based codes are less likely to work on highly optimized games as it requires stealing CPU time one way or another.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


